snippet: J.A. Happ gave up three runs, three hits and four walks over 2 2-3 innings, but Jose Bautista bailed him out, hitting two homers to lead the Toronto Blue Jays over the Philadelphia Phillies 11-6 Wednesday....

headline.print_headline: Happ Struggles in Jays' 11-6 Win Over Phils
headline.main: Happ Struggles in Jays' 11-6 Win Over Phils

lead_paragraph: J.A. Happ gave up three runs, three hits and four walks over 2 2-3 innings, but Jose Bautista bailed him out, hitting two homers to lead the Toronto Blue Jays over the Philadelphia Phillies 11-6 Wednesday.
